            "answer_text": "Just build your application like u want, then use one of the excel packages available: XlsxWriter (writes excel files and charts)Xlwt (writing)Xlrd (read from excel files)Openpyxl (read/write)If your application manipulates a lot of data, i suggest you to use Pandas.Pandas makes reading and writing excel files very easy, but it comes with the cost of learning a big library.Hope it helps! ",
